== Welcome to Trackster

A simple (and only in early development) web analytics server.

Internal search
	Configure a parameter for the web property that represents the internal search result
	In analyser, check the url for that parameter and use as internal search terms;
	Can't use existing search terms because that's how you found this page - so could be
	both external and internal search terms for a given page
	
to_chart(x, y, options)
x and y represent methods called on the result set
use formatters if they exist for their formatting
applies to tooltips and labels

options
:type =>
:title
:height
:width

Some way to fill in a data series	ie. fill the gaps where data does not exist


Import email, recode anchors, auto-create redirects (part of campaign management)